[%- uri = c.uri_for('verify') _ '/' _ user.id _ '/' _ user.token %]
<p>Hello,</p>
<p>
	You have been signed up to <a href="[% c.uri_for('/') %]">[% name %]</a>
	with the following credentials:
</p>
<ul>
	<li><strong>Username: </strong>[% c.form.valid.username %]</strong></li>
	<li><strong>Password: </strong>[% c.form.valid.password %]</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><a href="[% uri %]">Click here</a> to verify this account.</p>
<hr />
<p>
	This email was sent to &lt;[% c.form.valid.email %]&gt;. 
	<a href="[% uri _ '?delete=1' %]">Click here</a> if you believe it
	to have been sent in error.
</p>